Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}我有预感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,420)}多彩的未来
